        Quickstart
        ----------
        
        Install ccc::
        
            pip install CCC
        
        Add it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            INSTALLED_APPS = (
                ...
                'ccc.apps.CccConfig',
                ...
            )
        
        Add ccc's URL patterns:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            from ccc import urls as ccc_urls
        
        
            urlpatterns = [
                ...
                url(r'^', include(ccc_urls)),
                ...
            ]
        
